description: The Deka MDAX UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the MDAX Index (performance index). The index includes 50 mid-cap German stock corporations and foreign companies with legal headquarters in the EU or EFTA or operational headquarters in Germany that rank below the 40 DAX stocks in terms of market capitalization. Admission to the MDAX is subject to listing on the regulated market of the Frankfurt Stock Exchange (FWB) .
name: Deka MDAX UCITS ETF
